{"tid":1621130,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Cloud Platform vpn","createTime":"2019-10-04T12:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T14:37:54.000Z","uid":177219,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"26b7bee73037203e135d61b6714be9cf6af4ef17","tid":1621130,"uid":177219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:30:29.000Z","msg":"以下係我一位IT 朋友教我整既Google Cloud Platform vpn, 原則上係免費, 但要信用卡註冊, 會扣你地1美金但會free 返比你頭一年免費, 之後會有300美金慢慢扣, 不過會係你同意情況下先會扣錢.<br />\n至於安全問題, google 就自己諗啦<br />\n1. 入<a href=\"https://cloud.google.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloud.google.com&d=HXevA6ue1FLA%2Fu9R3J04LnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=7fcac942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cloud.google.com</a><br />\n2. 用google account登入<br />\n3. 按右上角&ldquo;免費開始使用&rdquo;<br />\n4. 登記完後按右上角&ldquo;控制台&rdquo;<br />\n5. 左上角按三劃的目錄》Computer Engine<br />\n6. 按上面&ldquo;建立執行個體&rdquo;<br />\n7. 區域選us-west1/ us-central1 / us-east1<br />\n8. 機器類型選&ldquo;f1-micro&rdquo;<br />\n9. 開機磁碟選&ldquo;Debian GNU/Linux 10 (buster)&rdquo;<br />\n10. 剔選&ldquo;允許HTTP流量&rdquo;及&ldquo;允許HTTPS流量&rdquo;<br />\n11. 按建立<br />\n12. 建立完成後在&rdquo;VM 執行個體&ldquo;頁，新建的VM列，按右方的三點》查看網絡詳細資料<br />\n13. 在VPC網絡頁，按左欄的&ldquo;外部IP位址&rdquo;<br />\n14. 將&ldquo;臨時&rdquo;改為&ldquo;靜態&rdquo;<br />\n15. 在彈出來的對話框隨意輸入名稱，按保留。請記下顯示的外部位址（e.g. 35.xxx.xxx.xxx）<br />\n16. 按左欄的&ldquo;防火牆規則&rdquo;<br />\n17. 按上方&rdquo;建立 防火牆規<br />\n18. 名稱輸入&rdquo;allow-shadowsocks&rdquo;, 目標代碼輸入&ldquo;https-server&rdquo;，來源IP範圍輸入&rdquo;0.0.0.0／0&ldquo;，tcp輸入&rdquo;443&rdquo;，udp輸入&rdquo;443&rdquo;，其剩保持不變，按建立。<br />\n19. 左上角按三劃的目錄》Computer Engine<br />\n20. 在&rdquo;VM 執行個體&ldquo;頁，按SSH<br />\n21. 在彈出的SSH console輸入<br />\n 將內容改為<br />\n23. Ctrl+O<br />\n24. Enter<br />\n25. Ctrl+X<br />\n26. sudo systemctl restart shadowsocks-libev<br />\n27. sudo netstat -nlp<br />\n28. 檢查443已在監聽<br />\n29. sudo apt-get -y install apache2<br />\n30. sudo nano /etc/apache2/ports.conf<br />\n31. 將所有443改為8443<br />\n32. Ctrl+O<br />\n33. Enter<br />\n34. Ctrl+X<br />\n35. sudo nano /etc/apache2/sites-available/default-ssl.conf<br />\n36. 將443改為8443<br />\n37. Ctrl+O<br />\n38. Enter<br />\n39. Ctrl+X<br />\n40. sudo a2enmod ssl<br />\n41. sudo a2ensite default-ssl<br />\n42. sudo systemctl restart apache2<br />\nAndroid手機<br />\n1. 安裝shadowsocks: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.github.shadowsocks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.github.shadowsocks&d=HXevA6ue1FLA%2Fu9R3J04LnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=ae7964e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.github.shadowsocks</a><br />\n2. 安裝simple-obfs: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.github.shadowsocks.plugin.obfs_local\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.github.shadowsocks.plugin.obfs_local&d=HXevA6ue1FLA%2Fu9R3J04LnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=84d53066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.github.shadowsocks.plugin.obfs_local</a><br />\n3. 打開shadowsocks app<br />\n4. 右上角按新增&ldquo;手動設置&rdquo;<br />\n5. 伺服器輸入剛才記下的外部位址（e.g. 35.xxx.xxx.xxx）<br />\n6. 端口輸入443<br />\n7. 密碼輸入 YOUR_PASSWORD<br />\n8. 加密輸選chacha20-ietf-poly1305<br />\n9. Route 選全部<br />\n10. 剔選IPv6 Route<br />\n11. DNS輸入1.1.1.1<br />\n12. 剔選DNS over UDP<br />\n13. 外掛選擇 Simple obfuscation<br />\n14. 外掛設定內obfuscation wrapper選tls, obfuscation hostname輪入剛才的外部位址（e.g. 35.xxx.xxx.xxx）<br />\n15. 選右上剔號保存<br />\n16. 在app的第一頁選剛新增的伺服器<br />\n17. 按下方中間的紙飛機<br />\n18. 再觸下左測試成功<br />\n19. 用browser訪<a href=\"https://whatismyipaddress.com/,\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwhatismyipaddress.com%2F%2C&d=HXevA6ue1FLA%2Fu9R3J04LnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=0a9e0827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://whatismyipaddress.com/,</a> 應顯示你的IP為剛才的外部位址（e.g. 35.xxx.xxx.xxx），在美國<br />\n利申: 係我朋友幫手搞, 大家有問題我都要問佢先幫到大家<br />\n最後我希望唔會有人需要用到 vpn 上網<br />\n香港人加油, 祝願各位平安"},{"pid":"845a3753f2410dd290f856100fbc81ba04fd8d21","tid":1621130,"uid":177219,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"有d code出唔到，係度補圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aGTqLAC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaGTqLAC.jpg&h=6e3e9450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第21及22項"},{"pid":"3d22b31edb3e07ef61f06263b33133a245cc9e49","tid":1621130,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:46:54.000Z","msg":"simple-obfs已經停咗支援，要用v2ray plug-in<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/M3chD09/shadowsocks-with-v2ray-plugin-install\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FM3chD09%2Fshadowsocks-with-v2ray-plugin-install&d=HXevA6ue1FLA%2Fu9R3J04LnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=30946373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/M3chD09/shadowsocks-with-v2ray-plugin-install</a><br />\n<br />\nios 嘅shadowrocket 都停咗支援 ，睇圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/svLQciB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsvLQciB.png&h=89cd3c88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dd4e63e795d6f20ad6483e9e902459a97259082","tid":1621130,"uid":177219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d22b31edb3e07ef61f06263b33133a245cc9e49","tid":1621130,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:46:54.000Z","msg":"simple-obfs已經停咗支援，要用v2ray plug-in<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/M3chD09/shadowsocks-with-v2ray-plugin-install\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FM3chD09%2Fshadowsocks-with-v2ray-plugin-install&d=HXevA6ue1FLA%2Fu9R3J04LnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=30946373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/M3chD09/shadowsocks-with-v2ray-plugin-install</a><br />\n<br />\nios 嘅shadowrocket 都停咗支援 ，睇圖<br />\n<br />\